#   (SHA-256 f0bb73814dd600c18393599fee6ce40181de737957af6c11f9316117266db88a).
#   This file changes ONLY the header comments (status/provenance/prerequisites). The
#   normalized runtime diff against that candidate is EMPTY — no value was added,
